{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.480", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.000", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.000", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Anliegen des vorliegenden Antrags, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.200", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Opferentsch\u00e4digung von Verletzten und Hinterbliebenen von Terroranschl\u00e4gen und anderen Gewalttaten deutlich zu verbessern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.240", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unterst\u00fctzt die Linke ohne Wenn und Aber. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.960", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das gilt nicht allein f\u00fcr die Opfer des Terroranschlags vom 19.\u00a0Dezember auf dem Berliner Breitscheidplatz; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.480", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn auch in anderen F\u00e4llen war und ist die staatliche Unterst\u00fctzung unzureichend."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.440", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich erinnere mich noch gut an die Debatte nach dem Auffliegen des NSU im November 2011. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.200", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich war damals Fraktionsvorsitzender im S\u00e4chsischen Landtag. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.160", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Entsetzen war partei\u00fcbergreifend sehr gro\u00df; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.280", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dabei waren noch nicht alle Verbrechen bekannt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.880", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr die der sogenannte Nationalsozialistische Untergrund verantwortlich war."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.960", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damals, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.040", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also vor gut sechs Jahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.040", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gab es von h\u00f6chster Stelle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.320", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "angefangen bei der Bundeskanzlerin bis hin zum S\u00e4chsischen Ministerpr\u00e4sidenten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.720", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diverse Versprechungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.120", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man werde alles tun, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.400", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um die Vorg\u00e4nge l\u00fcckenlos aufzuarbeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.040", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verantwortliche f\u00fcr die grauenhaften Taten zur Rechenschaft zu ziehen und die Hinterbliebenen staatlicherseits zu unterst\u00fctzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.920", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viele dieser Zusagen sind leider bis heute nicht eingel\u00f6st worden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.880", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr uns als Linke steht fest: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.920", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das derzeit g\u00fcltige Opferentsch\u00e4digungsgesetz muss dringend \u00fcberarbeitet werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.320", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es darf zum Beispiel nicht l\u00e4nger so sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.120", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Beweislast am Ende bei den Gesch\u00e4digten liegt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.400", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Weitere Punkte hat der Kollege von der FDP eben richtigerweise angesprochen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.560", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zwar hat der Bundestag in der letzten Legislaturperiode einstimmig ein Gesetz zur Einf\u00fchrung eines Anspruchs auf Hinterbliebenengeld verabschiedet\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.520", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist positiv\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.840", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber am 18.\u00a0Mai zugleich gegen die Stimmen von Linken und Gr\u00fcnen den Entwurf zur \u00c4nderung des Opferentsch\u00e4digungsgesetzes abgelehnt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.200", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu ein Zitat aus der Beschlussempfehlung:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.760", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Fraktion der CDU/CSU machte geltend, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.760", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass \u2026 in der Folge des schrecklichen Attentates auf dem Berliner Breitscheidplatz allen Opfern bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.960", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihren Hinterbliebenen geholfen werden konnte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.680", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daher gebe es \u2026 keinen akuten Regelungsbedarf."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.720", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was f\u00fcr eine fatale Fehleinsch\u00e4tzung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.920", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kann ich da nur sagen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.920", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch Herr Beck sieht das offenkundig anders, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.800", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sonst brauchte es den vorliegenden Antrag heute nicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.720", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Staat ist und bleibt hier in der Verantwortung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.000", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei dem f\u00fcrchterlichen Anschlag auf dem Breitscheidplatz geht es nicht um die Strafverfolgung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.200", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn der T\u00e4ter ist tot. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.960", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber bis heute hat noch niemand die politische Verantwortung f\u00fcr das schier unglaubliche Beh\u00f6rdenversagen im Fall Amri \u00fcbernommen und entsprechende Konsequenzen gezogen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.160", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dass die Angeh\u00f6rigen der Opfer dar\u00fcber w\u00fctend sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.080", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kann ich sehr gut verstehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.840", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es hapert nicht nur bei der juristischen und politischen Aufarbeitung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.600", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch bei der psychologischen Unterst\u00fctzung und der finanziellen Entsch\u00e4digung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.640", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei ist sicherlich uns allen klar: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.320", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kein noch so hoher Geldbetrag kann den Verlust der Toten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.680", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kann das Leid der Verletzten und Angeh\u00f6rigen wirklich ausgleichen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.720", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und dennoch brauchen wir endlich eine Entsch\u00e4digungsregelung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.640", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die diesen Namen halbwegs verdient. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.720", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der vorliegende Antrag k\u00f6nnte dazu einen Beitrag leisten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.400", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb werden wir ihm auch zustimmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.480", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe eingangs \u00fcber die Debatte im S\u00e4chsischen Landtag zum NSU gesprochen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.200", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damals gab es dazu einen gemeinsamen Entschlie\u00dfungsantrag von CDU, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.920", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Linken und SPD, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.560", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was in Sachsen wahrlich nicht immer selbstverst\u00e4ndlich war. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.400", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir als Linke h\u00e4tten gerne auch den jetzt zur Abstimmung stehenden Antrag mitgezeichnet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.880", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kauder hat ganz offenbar vergessen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.680", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "uns diesbez\u00fcglich anzusprechen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.040", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bin ganz sicher, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.600", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kauder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.480", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Angeh\u00f6rigen der Opfer vom Breitscheidplatz haben f\u00fcr derartige parteipolitische Spielchen kein Verst\u00e4ndnis."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.360", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein letzter Punkt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.640", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im vorliegenden Antrag ist ganz oft die Rede davon, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.640", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass etwas gepr\u00fcft und vielleicht irgendwann sp\u00e4ter vorgelegt werden soll. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.200", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Fraktion und ich meinen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.280", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen keine weiteren Ank\u00fcndigungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.360", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit denen die Betroffenen hingehalten werden; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.160", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir brauchen eine schnelle und durchgreifende \u00c4nderung der geltenden Regeln. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.120", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr steht Die Linke."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.600", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.000", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr B\u00fcndnis\u00a090/Die Gr\u00fcnen spricht nun Katrin G\u00f6ring-Eckardt."
   ]
  }
 ]
}